The three people accused of kidnapping 6-year-old Amy’Leigh de Jager outside her school on September 2, 2019 will appear in the Vanderbijlpark Magistrate's Court on Thursday, to apply for bail. Watch. JOHANNESBURG - Three people, including a teacher, are expected back in the Vanderbijlpark Magistrates Court today for formal bail application. The trio are accused of kidnapping six-year-old Grade R pupil Amy’Leigh de Jager, outside her school. 